## ğŸ§© Example 1: React (Vite) â€” Without Nginx

```dockerfile
# Stage 1 - Build
FROM node:18-alpine AS build
WORKDIR /app
COPY package*.json ./
RUN npm install
COPY . .
RUN npm run build

# Stage 2 - Run (simple Node serve)
EXPOSE 5173
CMD ["npm", "run", "dev"]
```

